Users Can:
*) Take Note
*) Edit Note
*) Delete Note
*) Search Note
*) Share Notes(View Only, users will be notified via email)
*) Need discovery of users for sharing notes
*) Notes can contain emojis, html formatted texts
*) Track of shared notes (i.e if the note is viewed then it should show viewed)
*) If the shared not is NOT viewed then a reminder email will be send
*) Notes can have tags(No private tags)

Models Needed:
*) Note
*) Tags
*) Email

API Needed:
*) Fetch All User Notes
*) Fetch All Shared Notes
*)